metadata.name: GASH Genesis
metadata.description: Gamania (GASH) is one of the leading entertainment companies in Asia and has over 10 million users by operating for well-known games such as Maplestory, Counter-Strike, and Lineage Eternal Life. Our mission is to build the connections between NFTs and blockchain gaming to the next level. The GASH GENESIS NFT is a collection of 1,888 membership pass that grants you access to future drops/benefits.
